<h2 id="contracts">Contracts: PandaDoc -- $49/mo</h2>

Franchise agreements, addendums, renewal documents, vendor contracts -- franchise operations generate a lot of legal paperwork. PandaDoc centralizes all of it with templated documents, e-signatures, and tracking.

The franchise-specific value is in templates. Build your franchise agreement template once with all the standard terms, then generate location-specific versions by swapping in the franchisee details. Track when documents are opened, how long the franchisee spends reviewing, and when they sign. Connect to GoHighLevel via Zapier so signed agreements automatically update the franchisee's pipeline stage.

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> $49/mo (Business plan).</p>

